place_info.title: Halal Wagyu Yakiniku Panga
place_info.address: 3 Chome-27-9 Taito, Taito City, Tokyo 110-0016, Japan

reviews.snippet:
大約晚上八點左右前來用餐，這間剛好在我住的飯店對面，看google評價不錯就來吃了
線上預約至少要兩人以上，但我只有一個人，不過服務人員仍然很親切的讓我入座
雖然每桌都有抽風機但效果有限，店內仍然煙很大，週遭聊天聲音吵雜，但我反而很喜歡這樣的氣氛，就像是日劇會看到的燒肉店氛圍，餐點是好吃的，相對價格也不便宜，食量大又有喝酒的人來吃大概會落在7000日幣左右
reviews.translated_snippet: I arrived for dinner around 8pm. This place was right across from my hotel, and I decided to go because it had good reviews on Google. Online reservations require at least two people, but I was alone. The staff was still very accommodating and seated me. While each table had exhaust fans, they weren't very effective. The restaurant was still filled with smoke and the chatter was noisy. I actually enjoyed the atmosphere; it felt like the yakiniku restaurants you see in Japanese dramas. The food was delicious, and the prices weren't cheap. If you're a big eater and drink alcohol, you'll probably pay around 7,000 yen.

place_info.title: Jojoen Ueno Shinobazu Entrance Branch
place_info.address: ＵＥＮＯ３１５３ ２F 1-57 Uenokoen, Taito City, Tokyo 110-0007, Japan

reviews.snippet:
平日中午自己一個人來吃
原本在沒有預約的狀況下櫃檯人員告知要等半小時，結果等不到五分鐘就被通知可以入座，真是意外的驚喜
每位服務人員都很親切，上菜跟收拾剩盤都很迅速，但不會讓人感到壓力，平日午餐來吃真的很高cp值
reviews.translated_snippet: I came here on a weekday lunch break by myself. I hadn't made a reservation and was told I'd have to wait half an hour. But I was seated in less than five minutes. What a pleasant surprise! Every server was very friendly. The food and leftovers were served quickly, but it didn't feel overwhelming. It's a great value for a weekday lunch break.

place_info.title: Dormy inn Ueno
place_info.address: 6 Chome-7-22 Ueno, Taito City, Tokyo 110-0005, Japan

reviews.snippet:
地點可說是非常好，離御徒町車站約五分鐘距離。
隔壁就是全家，10公尺內有好吃的拉麵跟燒肉，想按摩也有好幾家，逛街更是方便，阿美橫町跟百貨都在附近。
房間空間很夠，行李可完全打開，頂樓的大眾池晚上隨時都能泡，泡完還有免費冰棒吃，幾乎無可挑剔。
可惜我住的房間地毯有股像是尿騷味的臭味，且入住期間是沒有免費清掃的服務，希望這個狀況只是例外
reviews.translated_snippet:
The location is fantastic, about five minutes from Okachimachi Station.
There's a FamilyMart next door, and delicious ramen and yakiniku restaurants are within 10 meters. There are also several massage parlors, and shopping is convenient. Ameya-Yokochō and the department store are both nearby.
The room was spacious enough for luggage, and the rooftop public pool was open anytime of the night, with free popsicles afterward. It was practically impeccable.
Unfortunately, the carpet in my room had a urine-like odor, and there was no free housekeeping service during my stay. I hope this was just an exception.

response.snippet:
感謝您選擇入住我們飯店，並分享如此詳盡的感受。
得知您對於地理位置的便利性、房間的寬敞度以及大眾浴池與冰棒服務感到滿意，我們非常高興。
同時，也誠摯感謝您提出關於房間氣味與清掃服務的寶貴意見。這並非我們希望客人經歷的狀況，我們會立即與清掃團隊確認，確保此問題不再發生。
期待未來能以更完美的狀態再次歡迎您，再次為您的東京旅程增添舒適的回憶。

ドーミーイン上野・御徒町
フロント
response.translated_snippet:
Thank you for choosing our hotel and sharing such detailed experiences.
We're delighted to learn that you were satisfied with the convenient location, spacious room, public bath, and ice cream service.
We also sincerely appreciate your feedback regarding the room odor and housekeeping. This is not something we would like to see, and we will immediately check with the housekeeping team to ensure this issue does not recur.
We look forward to welcoming you again in the future, creating even more pleasant memories for your Tokyo trip.

Domile Inn Ueno Okachimachi
Floonto

place_info.title: Tokyo Skytree
place_info.address: 1 Chome-1-2 Oshiage, Sumida City, Tokyo 131-0045, Japan

reviews.snippet:
欣賞日本夜景的經典景點之一，樓下的商場也很好逛
這次買了可以去最頂層的票，喜歡看夜景但又有懼高症的我是一邊抖一邊看，但最頂層看出去的遮蔽物比較多，想拍到好看的夜景照可能要花點心思，下次再去應該買一般的票就好
reviews.translated_snippet: One of the classic spots for enjoying Japan's nightscape, the shopping mall downstairs is also quite enjoyable. This time, I bought a ticket that allowed me to go to the top floor. As someone who loves nightscapes but is afraid of heights, I was shaking as I watched. However, the view from the top floor is quite obstructed, so taking good night photos might require some effort. I'll probably buy the standard ticket next time I go.
